It can help users fill in information in the specified format, quickly generate calendar files that meet the system calendar standards, and integrate them into the system interface.
Users do not need to use the graphical interface to fill in any information, just fill in according to the specified format.
Due to the use of a system calendar, it has multi-platform compatibility and can enjoy system level notification functions. After sync with iCloud etc., users can easily use it on various devices or integrations, including Apple Watch and XiaoMi Smart Assistant.